<li id="cite_note-5">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Reviews of <i>The Spirit of Capitalism</i>
<ul>
<li>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFJones2002" class="citation journal cs1">Jones, Eric (2002). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/3217355">"Review of The Spirit of Capitalism: Nationalism and Economic Growth"</a>. <i>Journal of Economic Literature</i>. <b>40</b> (4): <span class="nowrap">1273–</span>1275. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://search.worldcat.org/issn/0022-0515">0022-0515</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Economic+Literature&amp;rft.atitle=Review+of+The+Spirit+of+Capitalism%3A+Nationalism+and+Economic+Growth&amp;rft.volume=40&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=1273-1275&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.issn=0022-0515&amp;rft.aulast=Jones&amp;rft.aufirst=Eric&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F3217355&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALiah+Greenfeld" class="Z3988"></span>
</li>
